---
title: "Funders - Find or Request Medical and Drug Repurposing Projects"
description: "Use CureAccelerator to discover research projects to fund or request research projects."
---
<section role="banner" aria-label="repurposing-research" class="page-header header--purple">
  <div class="header-content__container role-page">
    <div class="header-content__left">
      <%= image_tag 'roles/funders-img.png', alt: 'Researchers', class: 'user-role-img' %>
    </div>
    <div class="header-content__right">
      <h6 class="title__inverse uppercase">Funders</h6>
      <h3 class="title__inverse">Why Join CureAccelerator?</h3>
      <p class="title__inverse">You want your dollars to create tangible impact and solutions for the patients you care about most. CureAccelerator provides a network of researchers and support options for individual funders as well as organizations, with a central focus on repurposing for maximum impact. Learn more about repurposing here.</p>
      <%= link_to 'Sign Up', 'https://beta.cureaccelerator.org/registration', class: 'button button--white button--header' %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= partial 'components/page-scroll' %>
</section>
<section class="callout--brown" role="region" aria-labelledby="about-cure-accelerator">
  <div class="callout--container">
    <blockquote class="text center">
      &ldquo;The Kahlert Foundation is proud to support Cures Within Reach because their research can create immediate impact through repurposing. This year we are helping to fund the CureAccelerator project to develop more awareness and funded projects between researchers and funders."&rdquo;
      <cite>Greg Kahlert, The Kahlert Foundation</cite>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>
<section role="region" aria-label="clinicians-features" id="page-scroll" class="page-section--container">
  <header role="section title" class="page-section--header">
    <div class="section-tag-border"></div>
    <h6 class="section--tag">What can I do with CureAccelerator?</h6>
  </header>
  <div class="page-section--body">
    <h1 class="title" id="clinicians-features">Do more good more quickly by tapping into a  global community committed to repurposing</h1>
    <p class="text">CureAccelerator’s community is composed of like-minded people who are dedicated to creating effective treatments through repurposing.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid-layout">
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon benefit">Benefit</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Benefit from scientific review</h5>
      <p>All projects on CureAccelerator are subject to independent scientific review to support your decision-making or supplement your existing process.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon work">Work</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Work together with others</h5>
      <p>Collaborate with like-minded funders to create greater leverage and support for the patient populations you care about the most.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon difference">Difference</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Make a difference with your dollars</h5>
      <p>Post a Request for Proposal (RFP) with your specific requests, and access a community of researchers and clinicians committed to repurposing. Or browse existing projects to find a match for yourself or your organization.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon global-3">Global</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Join a global community</h5>
      <p>CureAccelerator is the world’s first online, interactive platform dedicated to repurposing research – a repurposing hub for people, knowledge and resources to connect in service to patients. Welcome!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<hr class="page-section--divider">
<section role="region" aria-labelledby="featured-users" class="page-section--container">
  <header role="section title" class="page-section--header">
    <div class="section-tag-border"></div>
    <h6 class="section--tag">CureAccelerator Community</h6>
  </header>
   <div class="page-section--body">
    <h2 class="title">Other User Roles</h2>
    <% link_to 'clinicians.html', class: 'card one-half shift hover' do %>
      <%= image_tag 'roles/clinician-img-2.png', alt: 'Clinicians', class: 'card--border__green-alt-1' %>
      <h5 class="card--title__green-alt-1">Clinicians</h5>
    <% end %>
    <% link_to 'researchers.html', class: 'card one-half hover' do %>
      <%= image_tag 'roles/researcher-img-2.png', alt: 'Researchers', class: 'card--border__green' %>
      <h5 class="card--title__green">Researchers</h5>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>